{"tid":972694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<一地兩檢> 高鐵女職員西九站「兩地」3遭非禮 警方指涉內地口岸籲報公安","createTime":"2019-01-07T14:24:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T14:44:16.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"96627d9faba7fa19cdb41bccbf67b8baa1b7c44b","tid":972694,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:24:10.000Z","msg":"高鐵女職員西九站「兩地」3遭非禮 警方指涉內地口岸籲報公安<br />\n <br />\n高鐵西九站一名23歲月台女助理，報稱在內地和香港口岸，被一名50歲男同事非禮，惟香港警方對於報案人在內地口岸區被非禮，僅建議女方向內地執法部門報案。<br />\n<br />\n「割地兩檢」後患無窮，繼內地法院人員至少2次在西九站內地口岸區拉人後，《蘋果》獲悉，高鐵西九站一名23歲月台女助理上周五（4日）向香港警方報案，指上月至本月期間在內地和香港口岸區，3度被一名50歲男同事非禮。香港警方同日在香港口岸區，拘捕該名涉嫌非禮的男子，但對於受害人稱在內地口岸區，亦遭對方非禮一事，只列為境外罪案，僅建議受害人向內地執法部門報案。有立法會議員批評，香港警方過往一直強調，與內地執法部門有協作機制，如今此案涉及兩地司法區，「係咪機制入到去高鐵站就會失效？」反映一地兩檢有漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》接獲消息指，1名高鐵男職員涉嫌在上月至本月期間，在西九站內3度非禮女同事，事發地點包括香港口岸區及內地口岸區。據了解，因應一地兩檢協議安排，「呢類個案，香港警方一般都唔會特別通報內地」，而按警方程序，亦不會跟進事主有否向內地方面報案。過去警方亦有通過警務合作機制，向內地警務協作單位尋求協助，但針對今次個案，本港警方並無啟動相關機制。<br />\n<br />\n香港警方回應指，西九站報案室於當日接獲1名23歲女子報案，指她上月在站內的香港口岸區，懷疑被1名50歲男子非禮。警方初步調查後，同日在站內的香港口岸區，拘捕該名涉嫌非禮的男子。他已獲准保釋候查，案件交由油尖警區刑事調查隊第四隊跟進。警方又承認，報案人報稱該男子也於內地口岸區非禮她，但僅建議報案人向內地執法部門報案，案件只列「境外罪案」處理。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵亦證實，一名服務承辦商聘用的月台助理，本月4日晚向車站香港口岸區警員報稱有人被非禮，但拒絕透露詳情。保安局則指，對此事沒有補充，重申根據一地兩檢安排，內地口岸區視為處於內地，內地執法人員有權按內地法律執法。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員譚文豪斥，今次事件不只是一宗風化案，亦反映一地兩檢漏洞，「喺同一個車站入面，遭受同一個人非禮，警方竟然話唔清楚，唔跟進受害人同一單報案」。他指，香港警方不知內地有否跟進，亦不會了解事主有否到內地報案，但過去警方一直強調，與內地執法部門有協作機制，質疑今次個案涉及兩地司法區，為何機制又不發揮作用，「係咪機制入到去高鐵站就會失效？香港人喺西九站入面，究竟點樣受到保障？」<br />\n<br />\n公民黨陳淑莊指，從此事可見，「割地兩檢」割走港人原在港擁有的權利及保障，壞處逐漸浮現，「因為非禮嘅地點喺內地口岸區，警方就只能『鼓勵』事主向內地方面報案」。她又稱，案情原本算簡單，「但就因為無端端喺西九，割咗一忽出嚟，做內地口岸區，我嘅保障又唔知道、權利又唔知道，甚至我向內地公安報案嘅程序都唔清楚」，擔心港人在內地口岸區遇事，亦不敢向報警。<br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"493a8e5263a2e4bb5e3ff767653884cac3481941","tid":972694,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:25:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e93545c42f4b93d2a8344837db0a96b3753968c9","tid":972694,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:25:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa57eaee2f7b5c000690958f43030e831651b9be","tid":972694,"uid":165136,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:27:25.000Z","msg":"新三不管地區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc699ebd030991dd7c5e9700f1c41272635d9c36","tid":972694,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:28:21.000Z","msg":"班狗淨係識白逗人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fafdec862ea28572c922ddefe07bdee6415f7a0","tid":972694,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:28:31.000Z","msg":"一X兩X全部都係荒謬"},{"pid":"60054f08eedf8b80c13001d54893bb6e4d26a472","tid":972694,"uid":51446,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:28:45.000Z","msg":"彈出彈入"},{"pid":"10abe60d41e7ff7d0f1be874c9f3773f2aeb3cb2","tid":972694,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:29:22.000Z","msg":"職員係內地區唔係照跟香港法律咩"},{"pid":"071fd2433e34b63c7526078bd6973926ed2c0934","tid":972694,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fafdec862ea28572c922ddefe07bdee6415f7a0","tid":972694,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:28:31.000Z","msg":"一X兩X全部都係荒謬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"一雞兩味？"},{"pid":"8b158e506a293d302093316e7c0508aefed862cd","tid":972694,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:29:38.000Z","msg":"黨鐵呢<br />\n死L左去邊?"},{"pid":"f793671453e64d674d3d1e6b76025b5993fb5f10","tid":972694,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"10abe60d41e7ff7d0f1be874c9f3773f2aeb3cb2","tid":972694,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:29:22.000Z","msg":"職員係內地區唔係照跟香港法律咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:36:45.000Z","msg":"跟？區區一個國家政府人員，使乜聽你小小地方官支笛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d712d8559aa44273f422568371bb3fc5d850be","tid":972694,"uid":156411,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:37:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20170726/s00001/1501062807317/【一地兩檢】中港法大不同-摸一下難構成猥褻-被偷金額太少不立案-梁美芬倡向內地執法者提酌情權\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20170726%2Fs00001%2F1501062807317%2F%E3%80%90%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%A9%E6%AA%A2%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E6%B3%95%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C-%E6%91%B8%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%E9%9B%A3%E6%A7%8B%E6%88%90%E7%8C%A5%E8%A4%BB-%E8%A2%AB%E5%81%B7%E9%87%91%E9%A1%8D%E5%A4%AA%E5%B0%91%E4%B8%8D%E7%AB%8B%E6%A1%88-%E6%A2%81%E7%BE%8E%E8%8A%AC%E5%80%A1%E5%90%91%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%E8%80%85%E6%8F%90%E9%85%8C%E6%83%85%E6%AC%8A&d=za12ywSivCnp80l6%2BeUfg8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ffaae7a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20170726%2Fs00001%2F1501062807317%2F%E3%80%90%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%A9%E6%AA%A2%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E6%B3%95%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C-%E6%91%B8%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%E9%9B%A3%E6%A7%8B%E6%88%90%E7%8C%A5%E8%A4%BB-%E8%A2%AB%E5%81%B7%E9%87%91%E9%A1%8D%E5%A4%AA%E5%B0%91%E4%B8%8D%E7%AB%8B%E6%A1%88-%E6%A2%81%E7%BE%8E%E8%8A%AC%E5%80%A1%E5%90%91%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%E8%80%85%E6%8F%90%E9%85%8C%E6%83%85%E6%AC%8A&h=2f666400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20170726/s00001/1501062807317/【一地兩檢】中港法大不同-摸一下難構成猥褻-被偷金額太少不立案-梁美芬倡向內地執法者提酌情權</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af79df0e8282b30a2c1ac82fb43eaf81310a904","tid":972694,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:40:29.000Z","msg":"在內地口岸區，一般行為受內地法律管轄。不過港鐵、西九站承建商、物料或服務供應商、上述單位的員工，以及高鐵乘客之間的合約或其他民事法律相關的事宜，都屬於「保留事項」，一般由香港法院依據香港法律處理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來刑事就要大陸處理"},{"pid":"5e68fd50e16a6d3072540f7610d6b04b5a025347","tid":972694,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3af79df0e8282b30a2c1ac82fb43eaf81310a904","tid":972694,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:40:29.000Z","msg":"在內地口岸區，一般行為受內地法律管轄。不過港鐵、西九站承建商、物料或服務供應商、上述單位的員工，以及高鐵乘客之間的合約或其他民事法律相關的事宜，都屬於「保留事項」，一般由香港法院依據香港法律處理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來刑事就要大陸處理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:44:16.000Z","msg":"咁好簡單，如果要令事件成為刑事，有好多方法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}